-- BG Group Lines Up $1.8 Billion Loan From Brazilian Development Bank BNDES
-- B y   W i l l   K e n n e d y
-- 2012-03-01T08:05:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-01/bg-group-lines-up-1-8-billion-loan-from-brazilian-development-bank-bndes.html
BG Group Plc (BG/)  received initial
approval for $1.8 billion of finance from the Brazilian
Development Bank to fund the company’s investment in offshore
oil fields in the Latin American country.  The loan, subject to a final agreement, will be allocated
to BG Group’s share of local construction costs for eight
floating, production, storage and offload platforms, the company
said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  